code: @Before public void setup() {     super.setup().     parameter = new Simplify(owner). }
@Test public void testWithDirected() {     parameter.configure(ParameterTool.fromArgs(new String[] { "--simplify", "directed" })).     Assert.assertEquals(Ordering.DIRECTED, parameter.getValue()). }

@Test public void testWithUndirected() {     parameter.configure(ParameterTool.fromArgs(new String[] { "--simplify", "undirected" })).     Assert.assertEquals(Ordering.UNDIRECTED, parameter.getValue()). }
@Test public void testWithNoParameter() {     parameter.configure(ParameterTool.fromArgs(new String[] {})).     Assert.assertEquals(Ordering.NONE, parameter.getValue()). }
